title: Modern Family's Ariel Winter kisses Levi Meaden | Daily Mail Online
text: comments Ariel Winter is dating an older man and she's not afraid to flaunt her love. In an Instagram post shared on Monday, the 19-year-old Modern Family actress shared a photo where she was kissing her 29-year-old beau Levi Meaden. The Sofia The First star said he was her 'man crush' as she went bra and underwear free in a skimpy slit mini dress. Loving him: Ariel Winter shared an Instagram photo on Monday of her kissing beau Levi Meaden. The actress also called him her 'man crush Monday' Ten years between them: He is 29 while the Sofia The First star is only 19 Wow: Here Winter shows off her bottom even more as her male pal flips the bird The 5ft1in beauty wore high heels as she pulled up her lips to plant a kiss on her new love. And the star looked sensational too. Winter wore a skimpy mini dress that had a spaghetti strap top section that showed off some sideboob. It appeared as if she could have been at another birthday celebration. The image may have been taken on this night: The teen celebrated her birthday over the weekend, sharing this clip of her cake Big treat: The looker was presented wit a large white cake with roses on the sides The number also had a slit up the side that revealed her upper thigh and hips. The raven-haired looker wore her locks down and straight and had her makeup and nails expertly done. Levi wore a black shirt and slacks and had one of his hands on her hip. This comes after the two looked good together at the Screen Actors Guild Awards in late January. He likes to kiss her: Winter and Meaden with Jeremy Maguire at the SAG awards They sure do look good together: Winter was gorgeous in a gold gown as her boyfriend wore a nice tux The star showed off her stunning curves in a plunging semi sheer lace gown in a shiny gold. The star talked to E! news in the red carpet where she discussed how she celebrated turning 19. 'I am 19 now,' the beauty said.
